cs.RO, cs.MA, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.ET 

The paper presents a new modular robotic system for programmable self-assembly, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The system also involves autonomous and distributed stochastic self-assembly, which can be categorized under multi-agent systems (cs.MA) and control systems (cs.SY). The use of the Hybrid Cube Model (HCM) and the solid-state actuation setup can be considered as artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and embedded systems (cs.ET), respectively.
